It also involves graph theory and combinatorics, which are common topics in computer science theory (cs.DS, cs.DM). The analysis of time complexity and algorithmic heuristics suggests a focus on computational complexity (cs.CC), and the use of proof systems and game theory suggests a connection to machine learning and decision making (cs.LG).
